entry.title: Peru's President Ousted After Attempting to Dissolve Congress
entry.content: The move to unseat Pedro Castillo came shortly after the Peruvian leader plunged the country into turmoil by saying he would dissolve the legislature to avoid impeachment. Vice President Dina Boluarte will take over.
